OL,3,CCharity supporting victims of human
OL,4,Ctrafficking sees 128% increase in
OL,5,Creferrals
OL,7,FA charity working with victims of
OL,8,Fhuman trafficking said it has seen a
OL,9,Fsharp increase in referrals this year.
OL,11,FFlourish NI, which supports survivors
OL,12,Fof modern slavery and human
OL,13,Ftrafficking, said it has seen a 128%
OL,14,Fincrease.
OL,16,FIt said it received 137 referrals in
OL,17,Fthe first 10 months of 2024, up from
OL,18,F60 in the same period in 2023.
