OL,3,CCharity supporting victims of human
OL,4,Ctrafficking sees 128% increase in
OL,5,Creferrals
OL,7,FThe figures emerged during the
OL,8,Fcharity's Hope Beyond Trafficking
OL,9,FConference, held during Anti-Slavery
OL,10,FWeek.
OL,12,FThe conference heard from one person
OL,13,Fwho shared their lived experience of
OL,14,Fhuman trafficking.
OL,16,FMeanwhile, the charity also revealed
OL,17,Fit wants to create a safe house for
OL,18,Fthose who have experienced human
OL,19,Ftrafficking, describing safe housing
OL,20,Fas a top concern for survivors and
OL,21,Fcrucial to their recovery.
