OL,7,FIt aims to open the facility by 2028,
OL,8,Fand said it will be operated by
OL,9,Ftrained staff to provide a safe haven
OL,10,Fto those fleeing exploitation.
OL,12,FJill Robinson, Flourish chief
OL,13,Fexecutive, said the increase in
OL,14,Freferrals demonstrates the importance
OL,15,Fof the charity's work.
