OL,3,CCharity supporting victims of human
OL,4,Ctrafficking sees 128% increase in
OL,5,Creferrals
OL,7,F"For more than a decade now Flourish
OL,8,Fhas been working with survivors to
OL,9,Fdevelop their independence, facilitate
OL,10,Ftheir reintegration into the community
OL,11,Fand help survivors to see a brighter
OL,12,Ffuture for themselves," she said.
OL,14,F"The steep increase in referrals which
OL,15,Fwe have seen this year only underlines
OL,16,Fhow vital this work is to the
OL,17,Fincreasing number of people in our
OL,18,Fcommunities who have experienced some
OL,19,Fform of human trafficking.
