OL,3,CCharity supporting victims of human
OL,4,Ctrafficking sees 128% increase in
OL,5,Creferrals
OL,7,F"We hope that our conference raises
OL,8,Fawareness of this important issue and
OL,9,Fdemonstrates the innovations Flourish
OL,10,Fis working towards as we continue to
OL,11,Fgrow."
OL,13,FStormont Justice Minister Naomi Long
OL,14,Fdescribed human trafficking as
OL,15,F"happening around us", adding it
OL,16,F"often goes unnoticed or is ignored or
OL,17,Fis hidden in plain sight".
OL,19,F"This issue requires a societal-wide
OL,20,Feffort if we are to successfully
OL,21,Ftackle this heinous crime," she said.
